00:00:39.990 --> 00:00:42.660 align:middle line:10%
>> REGINA: Dr. Bradley Nelson,
creator of the Emotion Code

00:00:42.660 --> 00:00:45.420 align:middle line:10%
and the Body Code is with
us once again to have a much

00:00:45.420 --> 00:00:46.890 align:middle line:10%
