depression in its wake.

00:00:54.660 --> 00:00:58.380 align:middle line:84%
Let's see how we can begin
to eliminate or overwrite

00:00:58.380 --> 00:01:00.840 align:middle line:84%
those programs lodged
in our subconscious.

00:01:00.840 --> 00:01:04.200 align:middle line:84%
And gosh, it all comes
down to that subconscious.

00:01:04.200 --> 00:01:07.800 align:middle line:84%
That pesky thing that's kind
of like a little bag of garbage

00:01:07.800 --> 00:01:10.030 align:middle line:84%
on our back, but
also of potential.

00:01:10.030 --> 00:01:12.570 align:middle line:84%
And so I think most
people don't really

00:01:12.570 --> 00:01:14.940 align:middle line:84%
understand just how
much our lives are

00:01:14.940 --> 00:01:15.940 align:middle line:90%
run by the subconscious.

00:01:15.940 --> 00:01:17.982 align:middle line:84%
And we're going to get
into that in a little bit.

00:01:17.982 --> 00:01:19.710 align:middle line:84%
But first of all, I
wanted to talk to you

00:01:19.710 --> 00:01:22.620 align:middle line:84%
