00:16:26.830 --> 00:16:28.830 align:middle line:10%
And that's one of the
beautiful things about it.

00:16:28.830 --> 00:16:30.920 align:middle line:84%
And that's what we really
encourage people to do

00:16:30.920 --> 00:16:33.260 align:middle line:90%
is get the book.

00:16:33.260 --> 00:16:34.380 align:middle line:90%
It's not expensive.

00:16:34.380 --> 00:16:35.180 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: Yeah,
start working with it.

