00:16:36.110 --> 00:16:36.630 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Absolutely.

00:16:36.630 --> 00:16:38.005 align:middle line:84%
>> NELSON: Start
working with it.

00:16:38.005 --> 00:16:39.980 align:middle line:90%
Learn the fundamentals of it.

00:16:39.980 --> 00:16:44.130 align:middle line:84%
And then you can start to remove
your own emotional baggage

00:16:44.130 --> 00:16:46.490 align:middle line:84%
and clear the heat wall
from your own self.

00:16:46.490 --> 00:16:48.050 align:middle line:90%
And families do that.

00:16:48.050 --> 00:16:51.410 align:middle line:84%
It changes the family
dynamics entirely.

00:16:51.410 --> 00:16:53.990 align:middle line:84%
Teams of creative
people do this.

00:16:53.990 --> 00:16:56.240 align:middle line:84%
And it changes the
ability of the team

00:16:56.240 --> 00:16:57.680 align:middle line:90%
to create synergistically.

00:16:57.680 --> 00:16:59.805 align:middle line:84%
And they're able to create
more than they otherwise

00:16:59.805 --> 00:17:01.400 align:middle line:90%
would have been able to.

00:17:01.400 --> 00:17:04.220 align:middle line:90%
But it's just a process.

00:17:04.220 --> 00:17:07.190 align:middle line:84%
Getting rid of emotional
baggage is something

00:17:07.190 --> 00:17:08.454 align:middle line:90%
that we can all do.

00:17:08.454 --> 00:17:10.829 align:middle line:84%
In fact, it's so simple that
kids can learn how to do it.

00:17:10.829 --> 00:17:11.450 align:middle line:90%
And they are.

00:17:11.450 --> 00:17:13.700 align:middle line:84%
And they're having really
good success around the world.

00:17:13.700 --> 00:17:16.200 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: Well, OK, so give
us an idea what that looks like

00:17:16.200 --> 00:17:17.337 align:middle line:90%
as a little kid.

00:17:17.337 --> 00:17:18.920 align:middle line:84%
Give us the kid
version of it and what

00:17:18.920 --> 00:17:20.760 align:middle line:90%
they would do in this process.

00:17:20.760 --> 00:17:22.460 align:middle line:90%
>> NELSON: Well, for example--

