Well, a great example--

00:17:51.505 --> 00:17:52.880 align:middle line:84%
I'm not sure if
I told this story

00:17:52.880 --> 00:17:54.955 align:middle line:84%
on one of the other
shows, but there

00:17:54.955 --> 00:17:56.330 align:middle line:84%
was a woman who
told me the story

00:17:56.330 --> 00:18:00.417 align:middle line:84%
that she got "The Emotion
Code" and started reading it.

00:18:00.417 --> 00:18:02.750 align:middle line:84%
And then her son started
reading it and listening to it.

00:18:02.750 --> 00:18:04.947 align:middle line:84%
And he started practicing
with his friends.

00:18:04.947 --> 00:18:06.530 align:middle line:84%
And she didn't pay
too much attention.

00:18:06.530 --> 00:18:08.123 align:middle line:90%
But a couple of weeks went by.

00:18:08.123 --> 00:18:09.290 align:middle line:90%
And one day the phone rings.

00:18:09.290 --> 00:18:10.160 align:middle line:90%
And she picks up the phone.

00:18:10.160 --> 00:18:11.810 align:middle line:84%
And there's a woman on the
other end of the phone line

00:18:11.810 --> 00:18:13.700 align:middle line:84%
who identifies herself
as the mother of one

00:18:13.700 --> 00:18:15.800 align:middle line:90%
of her son's friends.

00:18:15.800 --> 00:18:18.927 align:middle line:84%
And she says, listen, your son's
been doing this emotional thing

00:18:18.927 --> 00:18:19.760 align:middle line:90%
with the other boys.

00:18:19.760 --> 00:18:20.930 align:middle line:84%
And she said, I thought
it was kind of cute.

00:18:20.930 --> 00:18:22.722 align:middle line:84%
But she said, I have
to tell you something,

00:18:22.722 --> 00:18:25.610 align:middle line:84%
she said, my son has a
severe phobia of water.

00:18:25.610 --> 00:18:27.960 align:middle line:84%
You can have a
phobia to anything.

