00:36:22.920 --> 00:36:25.440 align:middle line:84%
It can find the truth
and the data for us.

00:36:25.440 --> 00:36:29.400 align:middle line:84%
We have a higher mind that
can set an intention in motion

00:36:29.400 --> 00:36:31.530 align:middle line:84%
that's capable of fixing
pretty much anything,

00:36:31.530 --> 00:36:32.880 align:middle line:90%
what we call miracles.

00:36:32.880 --> 00:36:33.840 align:middle line:90%
All of it's there.

00:36:33.840 --> 00:36:35.070 align:middle line:90%
We possess all of it.

00:36:35.070 --> 00:36:39.030 align:middle line:90%
And a body set up to self-heal.

00:36:39.030 --> 00:36:40.920 align:middle line:90%
And yet look how sick we are.

00:36:40.920 --> 00:36:47.430 align:middle line:84%
So why is this information
kind of so remote and seemingly

00:36:47.430 --> 00:36:50.370 align:middle line:90%
hidden from us?

00:36:50.370 --> 00:36:57.000 align:middle line:84%
>> NELSON: Well, I think that
in the same way that we've kind

00:36:57.000 --> 00:37:00.490 align:middle line:84%
