00:37:35.700 --> 00:37:39.990 align:middle line:84%
those beliefs to see where
those have really come from

00:37:39.990 --> 00:37:42.780 align:middle line:84%
and who was funding
those beliefs,

00:37:42.780 --> 00:37:47.370 align:middle line:84%
then I think that that
is a place to start,

00:37:47.370 --> 00:37:55.060 align:middle line:84%
where we need to shift our
systems of absorbing knowledge.

00:37:55.060 --> 00:37:58.470 align:middle line:84%
And I think that we
need to start really

00:37:58.470 --> 00:38:01.860 align:middle line:84%
looking inward and
trusting our own intuition

00:38:01.860 --> 00:38:06.270 align:middle line:84%
